---
title: Blueberry BBQ Pork Chops with Sweet Potato Rounds
description: A sweet twist to BBQ sauce may sound unexpected but believe us: it's a match made in heaven! Blueberry jam and BBQ sauce combine for a sticky, smoky-sweet pork chop coating. Roasted sweet potato rounds and a green bean and cherry tomato medley round out this meal with a rainbow of colours!
